    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You invoke the fire of demons within your lungs, allowing you to spew it out like one. Until the jutsu ends, you can use an action to exhale fire in a 45-foot cone. Each creature in that area must make a Dexterity saving throw, taking 8d6+8 fire damage and inflicting a rank of burned on a failed save, or half as much damage and no additional effects on a successful one.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above <br />A-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and increase the damage by 1d6+1.</p>",
